NAALALA NIYO BA SI TYSON? Ang batang binigyan ni CramBayan ng Bike nung panahong nasa maliit palang kaming lamesa. Ito na siya ngayon at binibisita tayo sa ating FOOD TRUCK. Hindi nakakalimot at hanggang ngayon nag papasalamat padin sa pag tupad ni CramBayan sakanyang wish noon. 🥹 💚

ANDITO NA KAMI SA PWESTO MGA SUKIIII! Sugurin niyo nadin kami gaya ng pag sugod samin ni tyson HAHAH! Big boy na siya. 

KITAKITS DITO SA PWESTO MGA SUKI 🚛

📍RMC STOR LERMA ST. (beside FEU MNL) 
⏰: 9:00am to 3:00pm
———————————————
NEW PRODUCTS: 

• 🥟🍫 5PCS CHOCO XLB w/ Seasalt Cream ₱120

•🍗🥗 CHICKEN CAESAR SALAD W/ SAUCE ₱150 

————————————————————————

Rice Meals:

•🐣👑 CHICKEN ALA KING ₱120

• 🐮🧄GARLIC PEPPER BEEF w/ Rice ₱120 (no pork)

•🧆🍟 ULTIMATE BURGER STEAK w/ Fries & Rice ₱120 (no pork)

————————————————————————
Pastas: 

•🍝 CREAMY SHRIMP PESTO PASTA w/ 2pcs Pesto Bread (no pork) ₱150

•🍝CHEESY BEEF LASAGNA w/  2pcs Garlic Pesto Bread (no pork!!!) ₱150

•🍝 CREAMY CARBONARA w/ Chicken Cordon Bleu ₱150 

•🍝 MAC N CHEESE W/ Chicken Tenders (honey mustard, garlic parmersan, spicy bbq) ₱150 

-PM ME FOR RESERVATION/ORDERS 🫶🏻

message.text:
Hi OPC,

Happy Tuesday! 💚 We’ll be opening a little later today, around 10:15 AM, dahil may konting equipment issues, but don’t worry—we’ll still serve you the meals you love.

Today’s Menu:
🍴 Chicken Parmigiana – ₱120
🍴 Chicken Curry Katsu – ₱130
🍴 General Tso’s Chicken – ₱110
🍴 Creamy Pesto Pasta – ₱120
🍴 Honey Glazed Pork Belly – ₱130
🍴 Beef Salpicao – ₱140

Thank you so much for always supporting us. 🙏 Hope to see you at Munchbox Express—let’s make it a sold-out day together! 🤗✨

Visit us at Munchbox Munch Box Express at Lerma Street beside Bro Sisig and FC Buidling.
